itle><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence Is Creating Ethical Dilemmas. How Would You Solve Them?]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div>告诉我们您对 ChatGPT 提出的一些最棘手问题的看法<!-- data-module-name="article.app/lib/module/wsj/breadcrumbs" --><main id="main" role="main"><div class="wsj-article-headline-wrap crawler"></div><div class="articleLead" itemprop="articleLead" data-sbid="WP-WSJ-0001095080"><div class="is-lead-inset"><div class="media-object scope-
